Nice place, comfortable ambience. 
Friendly doctor and staff. 
Painless tretment sonfwr in 2 sessions. ( Hopefully  see the treatment is same after completing all sessions)

Well I did have an intense dental treatment with them . The entire dental journey was a joyful treat . The very first time I approached boosted my confidence to go for the entire treatment right away at the spur . The expertise and confidence with which they treated me was excellent . All my frontal caps had been replaced do good that they look so natural . They polished my smile 😊

Doctor is really sweet. Even though i had to remove my wisdom tooth he made sure that the pain was minimum. Trust him with your teeth. Also very smooth with surgeries. The clinic is really clean and neat. I love the couches. Must visit for any Dental problem.

Dr. Mohit was very pleasant, friendly in his approach. He explained the issues and suggested the precautions in a realistic way. He was very smooth with his treatment process and did not cause any discomfort. He seems to be a very good dentist and I was impressed even if it was my first time. Thank you Dr.

Let me describe this in one word first the experience was so HAPPY. From entering the clinic and carrying all those myths of the process of root Canal or cavity filling or injections being painful went off as soon as I was here. Dr.Mohit is so experienced and passionate about this, he says it's his thing.  To take my worries aways he played Arijit Singh songs and most importantly being patient with my nervousness. Who knew A tooth decay correction could be such a happy story. The injections are painless believe me if Dr.Mohit is giving it. I have found my dentist. Find yours here too. Special mention to how sweet Dr.Shaily Is.

PS. He loves Biggboss.🙋
He was very friendly and was quick with his work . They have a tv on the ceiling which is a life saver.
Excellent experience,  he did the painless treatment  of my teeth which was in severe pain. I recommend him for ********* painless root canal treatment.
Doctor did not give proper receipt for his charges so I couldn't get reimbursement...on requesting he stops responding messages
Dr Mohit explained very well and advised for future course of action. Till now I am not feeling any pain.
A great expirence with Dr mohit and team . Would really love to attend treatments again and again  with orthosquare . Thankyou so much
